      • VMProperties

        public VMProperties​(String pathname,
                    boolean loadFromXmlFile)
             throws Exception
        Construction from file or it takes the default values. Use storeToXML() to store the properties in a file.
        Parameters:
        pathname - the path to the properties file
        loadFromXmlFile - if true, use loadFromXML()to load the properties, otherwise construct the properties with (almost empty) defaults
        Throws:
        Exception
